Suede Bear
{{stub}}
[[Image:Suedebearcar.jpg|thumb|300px|Watch out America!]]
[http://suede-bear.livejournal.com/profile Suede Bear] is possibly the [[internet tough guy|hardest motherfucker who ever lived]]. Like all wicked men he has given himself a nickname which will strike terror into the hearts of his enemies - the [[Plushie|Teddy Bear]].
On the front of his LJ profile is a small piece of text:

{{squote|The truth is ugly, thats why we lock our prophets up in prison.|Charles Manson}}

So just like his hero, '''Suede Bear''' goes to prove that he is a [[dumbass|misunderstood yet brave and heroic]] individual, just like the [[Nazis]], Communists and Mr. Charles Manson himself.

==Mr. Bear Himself==
[[Image:Suedefursona.png|thumb|His fursona is slightly less hairy than he is.]]
Mr. Teddy combines everything all the sickest of the sick aspects of the [[furry]] fandom, including but not limited to:

*[[Babyfur]]
*[[Nazifur]]
*[[Bakedfurs]]

Any [[mundane|normal person]] left in the world which have the picture of a small, sweet-looking bear cub dressed in a [[Nazi]] uniform, smoking a [[drugs|doobie]] and sitting in his own [[shit]].

'''Suede Bear''' is also a [[fat]] [[faggot]], an [[alcoholic]] and a [[drugs|drug addict]] as well as having a fetish for piercings and [[Nazi]] uniforms. His attempts to prove how fucking badass he is are only emphasised by the fact he also likes to pretend he's a baby bear cub and swears at anyone who dares to suggest otherwise.

It's quite possible '''Suede Bear''' [[an hero|will not be with us for very long]]. Not only is he is a heavy drinker with heart and kidney problems, his [[BFF|boyfriend]] has also left him and his father is on the verge of death. So just like [[TheAmazingAtheist]] - another bear wallowing in his own [[shit]] - he decides to declare his stupidity on the internet.

Strangely '''Suede Bear''' also claims to be a mullato - which may explain his love of [[Nazi|Nazism]] and why he's as white as the spunk splattered all over his bedsheets. But if a faggot can love a [[Nazi]] why not a black person too?

==Discovery==

Recently another LJ user called miriena found this big ol' bear wandering aimlessly around the internet mumbling something about watching Captain Kangaroo having an enema, and decided to post this steaming sack of [[lulz]] for the rest of the web to laugh at.

However like all the baddest, meanest, cruelest men who have ever walked the planet '''Suede Bear''' will block users who write nasty things on his journal. That'll show 'em.

===How do I Spike Arms?===

Recently Seude Bear has announced he wants to [http://community.livejournal.com/bodymods/1855148.html implant spikes in his arms down to the bone]. There have been a few suggested reasons as to why he would do such a thing:

* To scrape the shit off his [[furry]] arse
* To slash his own throat open
* To open the caps on his beer bottles
* To help hang himself on his custom-made crucifix
* To help hang onto his buddies during [[buttsecks]]

